    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, making it perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. It runs great and is just waiting for a new home. I've truly enjoyed driving this beauty, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
