    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains its signature poise with factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Mechanical integrity is prioritized, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent clutch replacement to ensure the M96 powerplant\u2019s longevity. While the finish shows light road patina consistent with its age, the technical vitals\u2014including oil pressure stability, cooling system efficiency, and synchro engagement\u2014remain excellent. A driver-focused example equipped with a communicative hydraulic steering rack and staggered alloy wheels.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
