    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect blend of reliability and style. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, complemented by wheels that are free of major curbing, though you will find the occasional minor stone chip from light highway use. Step inside to a cabin that feels fresh and inviting; the upholstery is free of tears, the carpets have been protected by floor mats, and the climate control blows ice-cold. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the power windows, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves it has never missed an oil change. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers the tight handling you\u2019d expect from a well-cared-for machine. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 36500.0,
